- Kumusta.

103
00:08:53,230 --> 00:08:53,830
Boss,

104
00:08:54,430 --> 00:08:56,200
May meeting kami
ngayong hapon kasama ang K Group,

105
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,810
