203
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:39,720
Gagawin.

204
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:40,860
Ah, hello, Tiya Nong.

205
00:13:40,890 --> 00:13:41,800
Kumusta.

206
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:45,340
Ang sarap-sarap ng inihaw na utak ng baboy na nasa dahon ng saging
na ibinigay mo sa akin kahapon.

207
00:13:45,380 --> 00:13:46,680
Hindi ako madalas nagkakaroon ng ganoon.

208
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,630
Salamat diyan.

209
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:49,610
Natutuwa akong marinig na nag-eenjoy ka.

210
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:52,810
Magluluto ako ng pagkaing hilagang Thai
para matikman mo ulit.

211
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:54,690
Hindi ko lang basta tinikman.

212
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:56,610
Pinupuno ko ang sarili ko kahapon.

213
00:13:56,930 --> 00:13:57,930
Kailangang mag-thumbs up.

214
00:13:58,630 --> 00:13:59,630
